{
  "stem": "11179.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They knew what we-- this day what the refugee community did as a community, mainly the younger people but also a lot of older ones.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Doctor, ?] any girl young girls-- yeah, they seen dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they never have worked on one and they had to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "On the street they set up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because if they saved some lives-- maybe not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they could have saved otherwise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They-- they did with what little first aid they had to help anybody on the streets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that you could be proud of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the Chinese did show appreciation very much that lived around us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "For-- we could hold our heads really up in the community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And even the Japanese, they had cut our building off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was a little light shining out in the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They cut the power off in our building and turned it on again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because that building, the building I was living in, had-- had a clinic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The first floor was occupied by-- by some people with TB and also a clinic was there, first aid clinic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they helped a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There were some-- I forgot how many.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But there may have been about 60 or so caskets on the soccer field back there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] casket [INAUDIBLE] Japanese or somebody brought them in and they picked them later on up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "People had died there, but they-- they didn't deny them first aid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They gave them first aid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They gave them whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They saved probably a number of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "A number of them they couldn't save anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But I'd say I was proud of that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So as I say-- the worst day, was in the other respect the best day.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
